  "texts": [
    "For example, a participant shared:",
    "van den Berg Open Praxis DOI: 10.55982/ openpraxis.16.2.640",
    "I use ChatGPT for creating lessons, and I agree that ChatGPT has made my life a lot easier when it comes to planning lessons and getting content and structure for lessons/content that I will be teaching (P6).",
    "It is also very good at writing scenarios or stories where you need them to be used in storytelling or case studies to enhance the students' learning experience.",
    "It can provide suggestions and answers on completing certain pieces of work, and it helps me with subject content questions (P1)."
